{"product_id": "12170", "page": 7, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2012-12-30", "text": "If you really want to blast to the past as far as GTA goes, I would recommend playing GTA2, as it has many improvements over the original GTA.  This is still a great game, though I was disappointed that the Steam release did not include GTA: London or any of the other expansion packs.  Those content sets really brought in some great humor to the series, which was later refined in GTA2.", "hours": 0.0, "username": "angrysquare", "products": 503, "early_access": false}
